{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_03_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央 2話 誰に頂点に立ってほしい？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir、レッスン後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After LizNoir's lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "マスター、これと同じのもう一杯ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ another one of these‚ please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 133.33333329999996,
          "startTime": 3.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 6.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こういうお店、よく来るんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you often come to places like this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 9.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "たまによ、そんなに飲む訳でもないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Occasionally. It's not like I drink a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしても飲みたい時にだけ一人でここに来て\n飲んでるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I only come here by myself\nwhen I really feel like drinking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 17.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "……そもそも一緒に来てくれる人がいないもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Besides‚ there's no one else who would come with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワは莉央さん以外、未成年ですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The members of LizNoir are all underage‚ except for Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 24.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……あら？　貴方、あまり飲んでないじゃない\nもしかしてお酒、苦手だった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh? You don't seem to be drinking much either.\nCould it be that you're not good with alcohol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、そんなことは\n仕事の会食もありますし、誘われたら付き合いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ that's not the case.\nI have business dinners and if someone invites me‚ I do drink some.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 36.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "女の子を誘ったりはしないのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't you invite girls?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "誘う相手なんていませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't have anyone to invite.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "謙遜ね。今の貴方は星見プロを取り仕切る\nチーフマネージャー様じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Humble‚ aren't you? Right now‚\nyou're the chief manager who leads Hoshimi Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 48.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺はただのマネージャーですよ\nみんなが、アイドルがいてこそです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just a manager.\nIt's because everyone is here‚ the idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 57.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "謙遜も度を過ぎると面白くないわね\n……今、私のこと面倒くさいって思ってるでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being too humble is not interesting either.\n…Right now‚ you're probably thinking that I'm troublesome.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 61.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "い……いえ、決してそんなことないですよ\nいつもとは違った莉央さんを知れて嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ that's not true at all.\nI'm glad to get to know a different side of Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……そつがないわね\n私と貴方だけなんだから、今だけは本音を言いなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly… You're quite flawless.\nIt's just the two of us‚ so speak your mind for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 75.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、本音ですよ。みんなが頑張ってくれてるのに\n俺が弱音を吐く訳にはいかないですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I mean it. Everyone is doing their best‚\nso I can't complain or show weakness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 83.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方はいつもそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're always like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 85.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈が生きていた頃も\nきっとそんな感じだったんでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when Mana Nagase was still alive‚\nI'm sure it was the same.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 90.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈がいた頃は、彼女に引っ張り回されて\nそれになんとか応えるのに、精一杯でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…When Mana was alive‚ she dragged me around‚\nand I did my best to keep up with her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 98
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "でも今は、もっと大勢の子達に気を配らないといけない\nプレッシャーは昔よりずっと大きいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ I have to pay attention to even more girls.\nThe pressure is much greater than before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、やっと言ったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ you finally said it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 109.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "弱音よ\n私と二人の時は少しは肩の力を抜いてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your weakness.\nWhen it's just the two of us‚ you should relax a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 115.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "貴方の仕事が大変なのは、私にだって見ていれば分かる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know that your job is tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bar-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 119.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_03_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "だからこんな時くらい\n私には、愚痴の一つでもこぼしてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ at times like this‚\nfeel free to complain to me‚ even if it's just a little bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
