      "text": "変わらざるを得なかったものね\n後輩は出来るし、いきなりバンプロを離れたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had no choice but to change.\nI have juniors now‚ and I suddenly left Van Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
