      "text": "今日の練習では、以前の莉央さんに戻っていた気がして\n……だから、黙っていられませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In today's practice‚ I felt like you were back to your old self‚\n…That's why I couldn't stay silent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
