      "text": "いえ、莉央さんは今のままでいい\n行き過ぎそうな時だけ、俺に止めさせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Rio-san is fine the way you are now.\nI will stop you when you are about to go overboard.",
        "id": ""
